goals.1: Find the inventors of World Wide Web (return IRI and name).
goals.2: Identify the BGP for hypertext system.
goals.3: Find all the hypertext systems born before the 1980 (return the IRI and name of the system and the inception date).
goals.4: Identify the BGP for computer scientist
goals.5: Find how many computer scientists there are for each continent (consider their citizenship). Return the IRI and name of the continent and the number of scientists for each continent.
goals.6: Find all the computer scientists who thaught at the University of Cambridge (return IRI and name)
goals.7: Find all the computer scientists who wrote at least 5 books (please consider only the instances of book, exclude "literary work" or other type of work related to books). Return the IRI and name of the computer scientist and the number of books.

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?name WHERE { wd:Q466 ?p ?obj . ?p sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 100
output: on focus list of Wikimedia project
execution_output: on focus list of Wikimedia project

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?inventor ?name WHERE { wd:Q466 wdt:P61 ?inventor . ?inventor sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 20

2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?name WHERE { wd:Q466 wdt:P31 ?obj . ?obj sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?name WHERE { wd:Q65966993 ?p ?obj . ?p sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 20

3.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?name ?born WHERE { ?obj wdt:P31 wd:Q65966993 . ?obj sc:name ?name. ?obj wdt:P571 ?born } LIMIT 50
SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?name ?year WHERE { ?obj wdt:P31 wd:Q65966993 . ?obj sc:name ?name. ?obj wdt:P571 ?born BIND(STRBEFORE( STR(?born), "-" ) AS ?year) FILTER(str(?year) < "1980") } LIMIT 50

4.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?name ?obj ?occupation WHERE { ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?person wdt:P106 ?obj . ?person sc:name ?name. ?obj sc:name ?occupation . FILTER(STR(?occupation) = "computer scientist") } LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?name WHERE { wd:Q82594 ?p ?obj . ?p sc:name ?name } LIMIT 20
output: said to be the same as
execution_output: said to be the same as

5.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?name ?occupation ?continent ?continentname WHERE { ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?person wdt:P106 ?obj . ?person sc:name ?name . ?obj sc:name ?occupation . FILTER(STR(?occupation) = "computer scientist") ?person wdt:P27 ?nation . ?nation sc:name ?country . ?nation wdt:P30 ?continent . ?continent sc:name ?continentname } LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?continent ?continentname (count(?name) AS ?namecount) WHERE { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q82594 . ?person sc:name ?name . ?person wdt:P27 ?nation . ?nation sc:name ?country . ?nation wdt:P30 ?continent . ?continent sc:name ?continentname } GROUP BY ?continentname ?continent

6.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?name ?uni ?uniname WHERE { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q82594 . ?person sc:name ?name . ?person wdt:P69 ?uni . ?uni sc:name ?uniname } LIMIT 20
output: CITY College, University of York Europe Campus
Faculty of Mathematics and Physics, Charles University

6.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?name WHERE { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q82594 . ?person sc:name ?name . ?person wdt:P69 ?uni . ?uni sc:name ?uniname FILTER(STR(?uniname) = "University of Cambridge") } LIMIT 20

7.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?authorname (count(?bookname) AS ?bookcount) WHERE { ?book wdt:P31 wd:Q571 . ?book sc:name ?bookname . ?book wdt:P50 ?author . ?author sc:name ?authorname . ?author wdt:P106 ?field . ?field sc:name ?occupation FILTER REGEX(?occupation, "computer scientist") } GROUP BY ?authorname LIMIT 100

SELECT DISTINCT ?author ?authorname (count(?bookname) AS ?bookcount) WHERE { ?book wdt:P31 wd:Q571 . ?book sc:name ?bookname . ?book wdt:P50 ?author . ?author sc:name ?authorname . ?author wdt:P106 ?field . ?field sc:name ?occupation . FILTER REGEX(?occupation, "computer scientist") } GROUP BY ?authorname ?author HAVING(count(?bookname) >= 2) LIMIT 20
